profile_positions.description:
- Preparing and delivering lessons in English to Arabic to English translation to third and fourth-year classes;
- Marking work, giving appropriate feedback and maintaining records of students' progress and development;
- Researching new topic areas, maintaining up-to-date subject knowledge, and devising translation technics and comparative stylistics related topics;
- Selecting and using a range of different learning resources and equipment, including video broadcasts;
- Preparing third-year students for qualifications and external examinations to join the interpreters group;
- Participating in and organising extracurricular activities, such as cultural and social activities, and sporting events;
- Participating in departmental meetings, teachers’ debates and gatherings.
